"<keyseq><key>Orko Modifier</key><key>F11</key></keyseq>."

#. (itstool) path: section/p
#: C/howto_tables.page:58
msgid ""
"<app>Orca</app>'s <link xref=\"commands_structural_navigation#tables\">table "
